        <mxCell id="5BOf5oXSLcgK6-mnbLjW-8" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="1. The application is used by 1.5B users on daily basis&lt;div&gt;2. based on daily active users&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;the system should be available 99.9999% times&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;availability&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;consistency&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;we can have eventual consistent system&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. high reliability&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
